{"tid":2032950,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"強國留學生濟留外地: 我都已經這麼聽話了，怎麼還是不行!","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:03:12.000Z","uid":257468,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7632fd7df0c80bbefbcc8257de9c841b1287a5","tid":2032950,"uid":257468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"「五個一」是指3月29日開始實施的「1家航空公司在1個國家內保留1條航線，1週不超過1班」，原訂實施至5月31日。有報道稱 &ldquo;五個一&rdquo;政策將延續至10月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n史上第一次，中國民航網被顧客罵到關了評論!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2020/05/22/9482500.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F9482500.html&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=a85b2357\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2020/05/22/9482500.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/data/news/202005/22/9cf2860700cea9c4103ec84040db8773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F202005%2F22%2F9cf2860700cea9c4103ec84040db8773.jpg&h=387b0afe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/data/news/202005/22/23fe520bb051b26dd286c004b9943388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F202005%2F22%2F23fe520bb051b26dd286c004b9943388.jpg&h=8aec37d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/data/news/202005/22/dcdaab59e8e3b5306912511ea6577713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F202005%2F22%2Fdcdaab59e8e3b5306912511ea6577713.jpg&h=3f57ff42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/data/news/202005/22/f69697d7ef1057d10f25568ec37c2b68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F202005%2F22%2Ff69697d7ef1057d10f25568ec37c2b68.jpg&h=c0cfa4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.wenxuecity.com/data/news/202005/22/6607e4b74dc75471dce1ee0cf3b9a88c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F202005%2F22%2F6607e4b74dc75471dce1ee0cf3b9a88c.jpg&h=7ba58d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共民航局「五個一」政策 留學生回國難<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/5/21/n12127823.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F5%2F21%2Fn12127823.htm&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=fd925ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/5/21/n12127823.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n李小姐感嘆道，最初大陸疫情嚴重時，留學生特別單純，大家一起往國內寄口罩，利用完了他們導致他們自己買口罩的時候又買不到，現在又不讓他們回去。<br />\n「當初成批成批被利用，<span style=\"color: red;\">往國內寄口罩的人，和現在不能回國的人，是同一批人</span>。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷這件事以後，李小姐表示，「我真的是覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">如果能夠選擇的話，我不會選中國國籍</span>。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，笑完大陸D韭菜，為終將成為韭菜的自己乾杯~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a62a4fb52bae94b4fec1d337c563a2d5ff6b62","tid":2032950,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔明呢D係咩政策<br />\n戰狼外交？"},{"pid":"b7b4ae3fb2d1a3a078aba507ffc667ce44c5739c","tid":2032950,"uid":257468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57a62a4fb52bae94b4fec1d337c563a2d5ff6b62","tid":2032950,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔明呢D係咩政策<br />\n戰狼外交？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"驚D留學生返來播毒，令原本的抗疫成果GG，所以嚴格限制回國人數<br />\n收你幾萬一張機票，經濟上勸退，有人落搭就順便割韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手買口罩的留學生慘成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />